<p align="left"><font color="#000080"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">
&quot;Nam ke, bazalwana, be ndingenakuthetha kuni
nje ngakwaboMoya; be ndinokuthetha nje ngakwabenyama, nje ngakwabazintsana
kuKristu. Ndaniseza amasi, andaninika kudla kuqinileyo; kuba nibe ningekabi
nakomelela, unangoku anikabi nako. Kuba nisengebenyama, oku nje kukhoyo phakathi
kwenu umona, neenkani, neembambaniso, aningabenyama na? Anihambi ngokwabantu na?</span></font>
</p>
