          USILUNGISELELE UBOMI BOBUKRISTU OBUGQITHISELEYO NOBUNESIQHAMO</font><font size="4">.
          
 </font></span></font></b></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div>
<ul>
  <li>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><font color="#000080">UYesu
    waathi, &quot;</font><font color="#0000FF">Mna ndizele ukuze babe nobomi,
    babe nabo ke ngokugqithiseleyo.</font><font color="#000080">&quot; (<b>Yohane
    10: 10</b>).<br>
    
    
    </font></span></li>
  <li>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><font color="#000080">&quot;</font><font color="#0000FF">Umdiliya
    ndim, nina ningamasebe; lowo uhleli kum, ndibe mna ndihieli kuye, yena
    uthwala isiqhamo esininzi, ngokuba, ningekum aninakwenza nto.</font><font color="#000080">&quot;
    (<b>Yohane 15:5</b>).<br>
    
    
    </font></span></li>
  <li>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><font color="#000080">&quot;</font><font color="#0000FF">Ke
    sona esoMoya isiqhamo luthando, uvuyo, uxolo, ukuzeka kade umsindo, ububele,
    ukulunga, intembeko, ubulali, ukuzeyisa, akukho mthetho uchasene nezinto
    ezinjalo</font><font color="#000080">.&quot; (<b>Kuma-Galati 5:22, 23</b>).<br>
    
    
    </font></span></li>
  <li>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><font color="#000080">&quot;</font><font color="#0000FF">Niya
    kwamkela ke amandla, akubona ukuba uMoya oyiNgcwele uhlile phezu kwenu; nibe
    ngamanqhina am eYerusalem, kwa nakulo lonke elakwaYuda nelaseSamariya, kude
    kuse nasekupheleni komhlaba.</font><font color="#000080">&quot; (<b>Izenzo
    1:8</b>).</font></span></li>
</ul>
<p><font color="#000080">
        <br>
<b><font size="4">UMNTU WOMOYA</font></b> - limpawu zobuatu sisiqhamo sokuthemba
uThixo:</font></p>
<div align="center">
    <table border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="4">
      <tr>
        <td width="33%"><strong><font color="#000080">NguKristu osesihtalweni.</font></strong>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Uphiwa amandia nguMoya oyiNgcwele.</font></strong></p>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Wazisa abanye KuKristu.</font></strong></p>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Unamandia ebomini bo mthandazo.</font></strong></p>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Uya liqonda iLiwizi ukaThixo.</font></strong></p>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Uthemba uThixo.</font></strong></p>
        </td>
        <td width="33%"><font color="#000080">
        <img src="images/law4.2.gif" alt="law4.2.gif (4586 bytes)" width="178" height="175"></font></td>
        <td width="34%" valign="middle"><strong><font color="#000080">Uthando</font></strong>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Uvuyo</font></strong></p>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Uxolo</font></strong></p>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Umonde</font></strong></p>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Ububele</font></strong></p>
          <p><strong><font color="#000080">Intembeko</font></strong></p>
