</div>
</center>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#000080">Umgama ezithi ezimpawu zibonakale
    ngawo ebomini uxhomekeke kumandla athi uMkristu ayithembe iNkosi ngazo zonke
    iindleia zobomi bakhe, nokuba uvuthwe kangakanani na ebuKristwini.
    Osaqlalayo ukuqonda ngemfundiso yoMoya oyiNgcwele makangadakumbi xa
    engekafikeleli kumgangatho wamaKristu esel' evuthiwe, anolwazi nanamava
    ngaie nyaniso ixesha elide.
    
    </font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="right"><i><font color="#000080">Kungani inkoliso yarmKristu
    ingenawo la mava obomi obugqithiseleyo</font></i></p>
    <center>

    <div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><b><font color="#000080"><font size="6">2</font><font size="4">.
          </font><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><font size="5">AMAKHOLWA
          ENYAMA AKANAKO UKUBA NAMAVA OBOMI OBUGQITHISELEYO NESIQHAMO SOBOMI
          BOBUKRISTU.</font></span></font></b></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div>
</center>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Umntu
    wenyama uthembe imizamo yakhe ukuze aphile ubomi bobuKristu.
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>A.</b>
    Kunokwenzeka ukuba akaxelelwanga, okanye ulibele ngothando, uxolelo,
    namandla kaThixo. (<b>Roma 5:8-10</b>; <b>Hebere 10:1-25</b>, <b>I Yohane 1</b>:<b>1&nbsp;</b>
    <b>2:1-3</b>; <b>II Petros 1:9</b>; <b>Izenzo 1:8</b>)
    .
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>B.
    </b>Unamava oMoya oyiNgcwele angamahla ndinyuka.
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>C.
    </b>Akanakho ukuziqonda yena ngokwakhe - uthanda ukwenza okulungileyo, kodwa
    akanakho.
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>D.</b>
    Akaphumeleli ukucaphula amandia oMoya oyiNgcwele ukuze ahlale ubomi
    bobuKristu. (<b>I Korinte 3:1-3</b>; <b>Roma 7:15-24</b>; <b>8:7</b>; <b>Galati
    5:16-8</b>).
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>UMNTU
    WENYAMA</b> - Inxalenye okanye zonke ezi zilandelayo, ziimpawu zoMkristu
    ongamthembiyo uThixo ngokupheleleyo:</font></span></p>
    <center>

