    <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">(Umntu
    ozibiza ngokuthi unguMkristu kodwa ephikelele ukwenza isoono, usenokungabi
    nguMkristu nje konke, ngoku bhalwe ngu <b>I Yohane 2:3</b>; <b>3:6</b>, <b>9</b>;
    <b>Efese 5:5</b>).
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="right"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><i><font color="#000080">Inyaniso
    yesithathu isinika icebo lokuphuma kule ngxaki.</font></i></span></p>
    <center>

    <div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><b><font color="#000080"><font size="6">3</font><font size="4">. </font><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><font size="5">UYESU
          WATHEMBISA NGOBOMI OBANELEYO NOBUNEMPUMELELO OBUSIQHAMO SAWO
          SIKUKUZALISWA (UKULAWULWA NOKONGEZWA AMANDLA) NGUMOYA OYINGCWELE</font></span></font></b> </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div>
</center>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Ubomi
    obuzaliswe nguMoya oyiNgcwele bubomi obulawulwa nguKristu, athi ngabo
    uKristu aphile ubomi kuthi nangathi emandleni oMoya oyiNgcwele.
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>A.</b>
    Umntu uba nguMkristu ngokusebenza koMoya oyiNgcwele, ngokuka<b>Yohane 3:1-8</b>.
    Ukusukela kwixesha lokuzalwa kwakhe ngokoMoya, uMkristu uthiwe wambu nguMoya
    oyiNgcwele lonke ixesha (<b>Yohane 1: 12</b>; <b>Kolose 2:0; 10</b>; <b>Yohane
    14:16, 17</b>).
    
    </font></span></p>
    <span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><font color="#000080">Noxa
    onke amaKristu ethiwe wambu nguMoya oyiNgcwele, asingawo onke amaKristu
    azaliswe (alawulwa ongezwa namandla) nguMoya oyiNgcwele.</font></span>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>B.</b>
    UMoya oyiNgcweie ngumthombo wobomi obumpompozayo. (<b>Yohane<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">
    </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">7</span>:37-39</b>).
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>C.</b>
    UMoya oyiNgcwele weza ukuza kuzukisa uKristu (<b>Yohane 16:13-14</b>). Xa
    umntu azaliswe nguMoya oyiNgcweic ungumlandeli kaKristu wokwenene.
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>D.
    </b>Ngokomyalelo wakhe wokugqibela phambi kokuba anyukele ezulwini, uKristu
    waathembisa ngamandia oMoya oyiNgcwele ozakusinceda ukuba sibe ngamangqina
    akhe. (<b>Izenzo 1:1-9</b>).
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><i><font color="#000080">Umntu
    angazaliswa niani ke nguMoya oyiNgcwele?</font></i></span></p>
    <center>

    <div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><font color="#000080"><b><font size="6">4</font><font size="4">. </font> </b><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><b><font size="5">SIZALISWA
          (SILAWULWA SIDE SONGEZELELWE AMA<span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">NDLA)
          NGUMOYA OYINGCWELE NGOKHOLO: NGOKO KE SINGANALO ULUVO LOBOMI OBANELEYO
          NOBUNEMPUMELELO ABUTHEMBISILEYO UKRISTU KUMKRISTU NGAMNYE</span></font></b></span></font></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div>
</center>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="center"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Ungazithabathela
    oku kuzaliswa nguMoya oyiNgcwele <b> khona ngoku</b> ukuba ngaba:
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>A.</b>
    Unomqweno ngokwenene wokulawulwa nokongezelelwa amandla nguMoya oyiNgewele
    (<b>Mateyu 5:6</b>; <b>Yohane 7:37-39</b>).
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>B.</b>
    Zivume izoono zakho. <b> Ngokhoto</b> bulela kuThixo kuba <b>eakuxolele</b> zonke iizono
    zakho ezidluleyo, ezelixesha nezexesha elizayo - ngokuba uKristu wakufela. (<b>Kolose
    2:13-15</b>; <b>1 Yohane 1; 2</b>:<b>1-3</b>; <b>Hebere 10:1-17</b>).</font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>C.</b>
    <b>
    Ngokholo</b> zifunele ukuzaliseka koMova oyiNgcwele nje ngelungelo lakho ngoko:
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>1.
    UMYALELO WAKHE</b> - Zaliswa nguMoya oyiNgewele. &quot;Kanjalo
    musani ukunxila yiwayini ekukhoyo kuloo nto ukuzibubisa; manzaliswe nguMoya.&quot;
    (<b>Efese 5:18</b>).
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>2.
    ISITHEMBISO SAKHE</b> - Uyakusoloko esiphendula xa sithandaza ngokokunqwena
    kwakhe. &quot;Kuko oku ukungafihiisi esinako
    kuye: ukuba sithi sicele into ngokokuthanda, kwakhe uyasiva. Ukuba siyazi
    okokuba uyakuva esisukuba sikucela, siyazi ukuba sinazo izinto ezicelwayo,
    esizicelifeyo kuye.&quot; (</font><b><font color="#000080">1 Yohane 5:14, 15</b>).
    
    </font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" align="right"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><i><font color="#000080">Ukholo
    lungabonakaliswa ngokuthandaza . . .</font></i></span></p>
    <center>

<p>&nbsp;
    <div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p align="center"><font size="4" color="#000080"><b><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">UNGATHANDAZA
          NJANI NGOKHOLO UKUZE UZALISWE NGUMOYA OYINGCWELE
          
          </span><br>
          </b></font></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Sizaliswa
          nguMoya oyiNgcwele ngokholo kuuphela. Noxa kunjalo, umthandazo
          wokwenene yenye indlela yokubonakalisa ukholo lwakho. Lo ulandelayo
          ngumthandazo ongawuthandaza:
          
          </font></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><i>&quot;Bawo
          Othandekayo, ndiya kufuna. Ndiyavuma ukuba ubomi bam bendibulawula
          ngokwam, ndaba ndonile njalo kuwe. Ndiyabulela ngokuba undixolele
          izoono zam ngokufa kukaKristu emnqamlezweni efela mna. Ngoku nje
          ndimema uKristu ukuba abuye athabathe isihialo setrone yobomi bam.
          Ndizaliswe ngoMoya oyiNgcwele nje ngoko <b> wayalelayo</b> ukuba ndizaliswe,
          nanje ngokuba <b> wathembisayo</b> eLizwini lakho ukuba uya kwenje njalo xa
          ndicela ngokholo. Ndicela oku egameni likaYesu. Ukubonakalisa ukholo
          lwam, ndiyakubulela ngoku ngokulawula ubomi bam nangokundizalisa
          ngoMoya oyiNgcwele.&quot;</i>
          
          </font></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#000080"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">Ingaba
          lomthandazo uchaza umnqweno wentliziyo yakho na? Ukuba kunjalo, qubuda
          uthandaze, uthembe uThixo ukuba uyakukuzalisa ngoMoya oyiNgcwele khona
          ngoku.</span><font size="4"><b><br>
          </b></font></font></p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><b><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font size="4" color="#000080">UNGAZI
        NJANI UKUBA UZALISWE (ULAWULWA WONGEZELELWE AMANDLA) NGUMOYA OYINGCWELE.</font></span></b></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Wakha
          wamcela na UThixo ukuba akuzalise? Uyazi na ngoku ukuba uzaliswe
          nquMoya oyiNgcwele? Wazi ngaliphi igunya?&nbsp;(Ngokuthembeka
          kukaThixo ngokwakhe neLizwi lakhe: <b>Hebere 11:6</b>; <b>Roma 14:22,
          23</b>).
          
          </font></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Musa
          ukuxhomekeka kwizimvo zakho. Isithembiso seLizwi likaThixo ingasizizo
          izimvo zethu, ligunya lethu. UMkristu uphila ngokholo ithemba)
          ekuthembekeni kukaThixo ngokwakhe neLizwi lakhe. Lomfanekiso kaloliwe
          ubonisa ubuhlobo phakathi kweyona nto <b> iyinyaniso</b> (UThixo neZwi lakhe),
          <b>
          nokholo</b> (ukuthemba kwethu uThixo neZwi lakhe), kunye <b> nezimvo</b> (isiphumo
          sokholo kunye nentobeko yethu) (<b>Yohane 14:21</b>).
          
          </font></span></p>
        <p align="center">&nbsp;</p>
        <p align="center"><font color="#000080">
        <img src="images/train.gif" align="center" width="450" height="101"><br>
        </font>
        </p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Intloko
          kaloliwe isenako ukuhamba nokuba alikho ikhareji langasemva. Kodwa,
          ingabubuyatha ukulinga ukutsala uloliwe ngekhareii langasemva, Ngoku
          kwanjalo nathi, nje ngamaKristu asinako ukuxhomekeka kwizimvo zethu
          okanye uvuyo lwethu, kodwa sibeka ithemba lethu ekuthembekeni </font></span><font color="#000080"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">kukaThixo
          nakwizithembiso zeZwi lakhe.</span></font></p>
        <hr>
</center>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="center"><font color="#000080"><b><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font size="4">UNGAHAMBA
        NJANI KUMOYA</font></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">
        
        </span></font></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Ukholo
        (ukuthemba uThixo nezithembiso zakhe) le Iona thuba angathi uMkristu
        aphile ubomi obulawulwa nguMoya oyiNgcwele. Xa uthi umthembe njalo
        uKristu amaxesha ngamaxesha:
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>A.
        </b>Ubomi bakho bungabonakalisa ngakumbi okwesiqhamo soMoya oyiNgcwele (<b>Galati
        5:22-23</b>), ngokunialo buya kufuza umfanekiso kaKristu (<b>Roma 12:2</b>;
        <b>2 Korinte 3:18</b>).
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>B.
        </b>Ubomi bakho bomthandazo kwa nokuphicotha kwakho iLizwi likaThixo
        kuyakucaca ngakumbi.
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>C.
        </b>Uya kuweva amandla akhe ekungqineni kwakho (<b>Izenzo 1:8</b>).
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>D.</b>
        Uyakube ulungele imfazwe yoMoya echase ilizwe (<b>I Yahane 2:15-17</b>);
        echase inyama (<b>Galati 5:16, 17</b>); nechase umtyholi<b>  (I Petrose
        5:7-9</b>; <b>Efese 6:10-13</b>).
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>E.
        </b>Uyakuweva amandla akhe okumelana nesilingo nesoono <b>I Korinte
        10:13</b>; <b>Filipu 4:13</b>; <b>Efese 1:19-23</b>; <b>6:10</b>; <b>2 Timoti 1:7</b>; <b>Roma 6:1-16</b>).</font></span></p>
        <center>

        <hr>
</center>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="center"><font color="#000080"><b><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font size="4">UKUPHEFUMLA
        NGOKOMOYA</font></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">
        
        </span></font></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Ngokuba
        ngokholo ungasoloko uluva uthando kwanoxoleto lukaThixo. Ukuba
        uyaphawula ukuba ikhona indawo ebomini bakho (umkhwa okanye isenzo)
        engayikholisiyo iNkosi, noxa uhamba nayo, unqwena ngokwenene
        ukuyikhonza, ngokulula bulela uThixo kuba ekuxolele izoono zakho
        ezidluleyo, ezelixesha nezexesha elizayo - ngokwesiseko sokufa
        kukaKristu emnqamiezweni. Banga uthando noxolelo Iwakhe ngokholo ukuze
        ube nobudlelwane nialo naye.
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Ukuba
        ubuye wathabatha isihialo setrone yobomi bakho ngenxa yesoono owona
        mkhwa wokungabi nantobeko phefumia ngokoMoya.
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Ukuphefumia
        ngokoMoya (ukukhupha uMoya oncholileyo nokungenisa umoya onyulu),
        kungumsebenzi wokholo owenza ukuba wena ube namava othando noxolelo
        lukaThixo ngawo onke amaxesha.
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080"><b>1.
        </b>Ukukhupoa umoya ombi - vuma izoono zakho - vumelana noThixo malunga
        nesono sakho umbulele ngokusixolela kwakhe, nje ngoko kubhaliwe ku<b> I
        Yohane 1:9</b> nakuma<b>Hebere 10:1-25</b>. Imvumo ibandakanya inguquko
        - ukutshintsha umkwa nesenzo.
        
        </font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#000080"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><b>2.</b>
        Ukungenisa umoya omtsha - nikela ulawulo lobomi bakho kuKristu, </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">ukuze
        wamkela ukuzaliseka koMoya oyiNgcwele. ngokholo. Themba </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">ukuba
        Yena ngoku ulawula, ekongezelela amandla, ngokomyalelo </span><font size="3"><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">okwa<span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">base
        - <b>Efese 5:18</b> nesithembiso sika <b>I Yohane 5:14, 15</b>.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span></span></font></font></p>
        <center>

        <hr>
        <p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><b><font color="#000080">UKUBA
        LENCWADANA IBE LUNCEDO KUWE NCEDA UYINIKE OKANYE UYIFUNDELE OMNYE</font></b></span></p>
</center>
        <p align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">Izigidi
        zezincwadana, &quot;SOWUKHE WAQAPHELA NA IHLEBO ELINGUMANGALISO LOBOMI
        OBUZALISWE NGUMOYA OYINGCWELE?&quot; sezisasazwe ngeelwimi eziliqela
        emhlabeni wonke. Ngenxa yaloo nto amawaka amaKristu sele fundile ngamava
        amandla nolawulo loMoya oyiNgcwele amaxesha ngamaxesha. Ngenxa yobomi
        obaneleyo obuthenjiswa nguKristu, abanamava abo nabo ngoku,&nbsp;
        banamandla okwabela abanye ngokholo Iwabo kuKristu. AmaKristu amaninzi,
        xa selefundile ngale nyaniso malunga noMoya oyiNgcwele afuna
        ukuzibandakanya ekuvakaliseni uKristu nokuncedisa ukuzalisekisa uMyalelo
        oMkhulu kwisiZukulwana setnu.&nbsp;<br>
        WILLIAM BRIGHT, president, Campus Crusade for Christ International.</font></span></p>
        <p align="left"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><font color="#000080">
        
        <span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">Sikhuthaza
        ukuba lencwadana ma isetyenziswe kodwa ukugcina umgangatho nokukhusela
        ukuba kungabikho zindawo zitshintshwayo, lencwadi okanye
        iindawoezithile zayo,azinakho ukuba zingapapashwa ngaphandle kwemvume
        ephuma kwi -&nbsp;</span></font></span></p>
